---
title: Southwestern-Spiced Chicken Thigh and Ranch Salad with Charred Veggies
description: Poblanos and corn pair perfectly with tender chicken in this tantalizing meal that comes together with our fabulous Southwestern Spice Blend. It's easy, fast and packed with flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cuisses-de-poulet-assaisonnees-a-la-sud-ouest-et-salade-e03be936.jpg
